 headlines. =E2=80=9CExpensive JPEGs?! LOL.=E2=80=9D Because at their most =
basic, they=E2=80=99re simple: they make digital media ownable and collecti=
ble, and people sometimes pay a lot of money for them.=C2=A0
DAOs sit a level above NFTs -- DAOs can own NFTs and create NFTs, plus do a=
 whole lot of other non-NFT things -- and have more transformative potentia=
l than NFTs. An NFT is a piece of digital media; a DAO could be a whole med=
ia company.
