g] decentralized publishing platform =E2=80=9Crevolutionizes the way we exp=
ress, share and monetize our thoughts.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0
Zora, Mirror, and Uniswap are all protocols, but not all protocols are nece=
ssarily DAOs, and vice versa. To understand the difference, let=E2=80=99s s=
tart by comparing a centralized platform and a decentralized protocol, and =
then we=E2=80=99ll move on to the evolution of a decentralized protocol int=
o a DAO.=C2=A0
