r an action if certain conditions are met, without the need for human inter=
vention.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">More simply, <strong>DAOs are a new way to finan=
