 governance and incentive systems to distribute decision-making authority a=
nd financial rewards. Typically, they do that by issuing tokens based on pa=
rticipation, contribution, and investment. Token holders then have the abil=
ity to submit proposals, vote, and share in the upside.&nbsp;</p><div class=
